trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **Navigating** event.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för den **Navigating** händelse.

trans-unit.source: These event arguments contain information about the navigation that was requested, and are passed to handlers of the **Navigating** event, which is implemented by the following: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> NavigatingCancelEventArgs encapsulates the following details of the navigation request: - **Navigation Initiation**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.NavigationMode%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Dessa händelseargument innehåller information om navigeringsfönstret som begärdes och skickas till hanterare för den **Navigating** händelsen, som implementeras av följande:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>NavigatingCancelEventArgs kapslar in följande information för navigering begäran:- **navigering inledande**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.NavigationMode%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.NavigationMode%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Content**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navigering innehåll**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Request**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navigering begäran**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation State**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navigation State**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>

trans-unit.source: This information allows you to both evaluate the nature of the navigation request, and view and update specified request details before navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: Den här informationen kan du både utvärdera uppbyggnad navigering-begäran och visa och uppdatera information om angiven begäran innan navigation inträffar.

trans-unit.source: Based on the navigation request information provided by NavigatingCancelEventArgs, or based on application-specific state or code, you can completely prevent navigation by setting the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property to `true` (by default, <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> is `false`).
trans-unit.target: Baserat på navigering informationen tillhandahålls av NavigatingCancelEventArgs eller baserat på programspecifika tillstånd eller kod, kan du helt förhindra navigering genom att ange den <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>egenskapen `true` (som standard <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>är `false`).</xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the content object that is being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en referens till innehållsobjektet navigeras till.

trans-unit.source: You can navigate to content using either a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] or an object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan navigera till innehåll med hjälp av antingen en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] eller ett objekt.

trans-unit.source: When navigating to an object, which occurs when calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, Content contains a reference to the content object that is being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: När du navigerar till ett objekt som uppstår vid anrop av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>och <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, innehåll innehåller en referens till innehållsobjektet navigeras till.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A> property will be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom kan den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>egenskapen `null`.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Object> reference to the content object that is being navigated to; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>referens till innehållsobjektet som navigeras till, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> object that is associated with the back navigation history entry for the page being navigated from.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> objekt som är associerad med historikpost för navigering bakåt på sidan som navigerar från.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating> event is raised when navigating from one piece of content to another.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating>händelsen höjs när navigering från en typ av innehåll till en annan.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating>

trans-unit.source: The content that is being navigated from is added to back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Det innehåll som navigeras från läggs till tillbaka historik.

trans-unit.source: You can set ContentStateToSave with a custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to associate state information with content in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ange ContentStateToSave med en anpassad <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objekt att associera statusinformation med innehållet i historik.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> object that is associated with the back navigation history entry for the page being navigated from.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> objekt som är associerad med historikpost för navigering bakåt på sidan som navigerar från.

trans-unit.source: Gets the optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation started.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar valfria data <xref:System.Object>som skickades när navigering startades.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: ExtraData can be used to pass context-specific data that is specific to a particular navigation.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData kan användas för att skicka sammanhangsberoende data som är specifik för en viss navigering.

trans-unit.source: ExtraData contains a reference to the object that is passed as the second argument when calling either <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData innehåller en referens till det objekt som skickas som det andra argumentet när du anropar <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Annars är `null`.

trans-unit.source: The optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation started.
trans-unit.target: Valfria data <xref:System.Object>som skickades när navigering startades.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the navigator (<xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref>) that is specified by <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*> is servicing this navigation, or whether a parent navigator is doing so.
trans-unit.target: Anger om Navigatören (<xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref>) som anges av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*>betjänar navigering, eller om en överordnad navigator tiden.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> value that is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the navigator that is specified by <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*> is servicing this navigation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Boolean>värde som är <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> om Navigatören som anges av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*>betjänar navigering.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*> </xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> is returned, such as during a nested <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> navigation.
trans-unit.target: Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> returneras, exempelvis under en kapslad <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> navigering.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"></xref> value that indicates the type of navigation that is occurring.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"> </xref> värde som anger vilken typ av navigeringsfönstret som uppstår.

trans-unit.source: The types of navigation that can occur are: - Navigating to new content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).
trans-unit.target: Typerna av navigering som kan uppstå är: - navigera till nytt innehåll (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>

trans-unit.source: - Navigating to the previous item in back navigation history (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).
trans-unit.target: -Gå till föregående objekt i tillbaka historik (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>

trans-unit.source: - Navigating to the next item in forward navigation history (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).
trans-unit.target: -Gå till nästa element i historiken för navigering framåt (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>

trans-unit.source: - Refreshing existing content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).
trans-unit.target: -Uppdatering av befintligt innehåll (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"></xref> value that indicates the type of navigation that is occurring.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"> </xref> värde som anger vilken typ av navigeringsfönstret som uppstår.

trans-unit.source: The navigator that raised this event.
trans-unit.target: Navigatören som utlöses den här händelsen.

trans-unit.source: While Navigator stores a reference to the navigator that raised this event, the navigator may not have actually initiated the navigation.
trans-unit.target: Medan Navigator lagrar en referens till Navigatören som utlöses den här händelsen, kan Navigatören inte ha faktiskt initierat navigeringen.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether this navigator did initiate the current navigation, inspect the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: För att fastställa om denna navigator starta aktuella navigeringen inspektera den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that is the navigator that raised this event
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som är Navigatören som utlöses den här händelsen</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> object that is to be applied to the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> objekt som ska tillämpas på det innehåll som har navigerat till.

trans-unit.source: TargetContentState will contain a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object if navigating to content in back or forward navigation history that has a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object associated with it.
trans-unit.target: TargetContentState kommer att innehålla ett <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objekt om navigera till innehåll i tillbaka eller vidarebefordra historik som har ett <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objekt som är kopplade till det.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> object that is to be applied to the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> objekt som ska tillämpas på det innehåll som har navigerat till.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] för det innehåll som har navigerat till.

trans-unit.source: You can navigate to content using either an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] or an object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan navigera till innehåll med hjälp av antingen en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] eller ett objekt.

trans-unit.source: When navigating to an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], which occurs when calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, Uri contains the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: När du navigerar till en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], som uppstår vid anrop av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>och <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, URI: N innehåller den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] av innehåll som har navigerat till.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A> property will be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom kan den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>egenskapen `null`.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Uri> for the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Uri>för det innehåll som har navigerat till.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: If navigating to an object, Uri is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Om du navigerar till ett objekt, URI: N är <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> object that is used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>objekt som används för att begära det angivna innehållet.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a Web request, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>är en abstrakt basklass som kapslar in en webbegäran och är oberoende av protokollet.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> and extends it with protocol specific state and behavior, including: - <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: För varje gemensamt protokoll, den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] innehåller en klass som härleds från <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>och utökar med protokollet specifikt tillstånd och beteende, inklusive:- <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] som använder den `pack://` schemat att begära programdatafiler (finns [resurs för WPF-program, innehåll och datafiler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] som använder den `http://` schemat för begäran-filer från webbservrar.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] som använder den `ftp://` schemat för begäran-filer från FTP-servrar.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] som använder den `file://` schemat att begära lokala filer.</xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: You can both view and modify <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> details.
trans-unit.target: Du kan både visa och ändra <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>information.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: WebRequest is `null` when navigation occurs by: - Using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> control.
trans-unit.target: WebRequest är `null` när navigation inträffar genom: – med hjälp av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>

trans-unit.source: - Calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> - Setting <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: -Anropar <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>- inställningen <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Navigating through HTML content in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.
trans-unit.target: -Navigera genom HTML-innehåll i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> object that is used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> objekt som används för att begära det angivna innehållet.
